Required R Packages

Install Bioconductor first:

install.packages("BiocManager")

Then install all required packages:

BiocManager::install(c(
    "SBGNview",
    "pathview",
    "org.At.tair.db",
    "org.Hs.eg.db",
    "AnnotationDbi"
))

Install CRAN packages:
install.packages(c( "xml2", "rsvg", "RColorBrewer", "tidyverse" ))
